Generic single-database configuration with async PostgreSQL support.

This Alembic environment is configured to:
- Use async SQLAlchemy engine
- Read DATABASE_URL from environment variable
- Support autogenerate from ORM models

Usage:
    # Generate a new migration (from apps/admin directory)
    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://... alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

    # Run migrations
    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://... alembic upgrade head

    # Downgrade
    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://... alembic downgrade -1
